lead_paragraph: Alexis Robinson scored 14 of her 16 points in the first quarter, Haley Smith added 12, and No. 21 Colorado jumped to an early lead and cruised past Idaho State 85-53 on Saturday night to win their eighth straight game.

headline.print_headline: No. 21 Colorado Women Beat Idaho State 85-56
